  "body": "I'm using Ethereum Wallet in Light Mode.\r\n\r\nAs Ethereum Wallet doesn't seem to update geth every time, every time when there is a new version, light mode does not find any peers, even after waiting for hours.\r\n\r\nAs soon as I update geth and run it in console it works again and is synced within minutes\r\n\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `1.8.0/1.8.2/1.8.4` (stable build)\r\nOS & Version: Windows\r\n",
